OL,2,MThe Universe in Electromagnetic Light:
OL,4,MFrom Your Phone to the Big Bang
OL,6,CAlexander Belyaev
OL,7,CSun 18:00-18:30
OL,8,CStage C
OL,10,GWhat do your phone, the night sky, and
OL,11,Gthe Big Bang have in common? They all
OL,12,Ginvolve light, in one form or another.
OL,13,GIn this talk, we will follow light
OL,14,Gacross the Universe and back in time,
OL,15,Gtowards the Big Bang. We begin with
OL,16,GEMF in everyday life - the
OL,17,Gelectromagnetic waves around us - then
OL,18,Gmove out to the light we receive from
OL,19,Gstars and galaxies, and finally reach
OL,20,Gthe Cosmic Microwave Background - the
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
